flowchart TD

A[Review Lab 04 Requirements, User Stories, MVP Features, and Wireframes]
--> B[Identify Critical Assumptions]

B --> C[Select MVP Experiment Type]

C --> D[Define Target Test Users]

D --> E[Prepare Experiment Script]

E --> F[Prepare Feedback Form]

F --> G[Run MVP Experiment]

G --> H[Collect Feedback and Success Metrics]

H --> I{Success Criteria Met?}

I -->|Yes| J[Continue to Final Prototype]

I -->|No| K[Revise MVP and Repeat Experiment]

K --> G